name: Peace Out Purple Frames
description:
I don't think there's ever been a phrase as commonly considered "cool" as peace out. Since who knows when now at this point, it's been a staple in American slang and unlike other phrases, this one never seems to be uncool with kids.

Peace Out Purple Frame initial mint limited to 10, initial way to obtain one is to be entered into a drawing when purchasing an OH YEAH Gold Frame. All unobtained mints after 6:30 PM Est on January fourth will be burned.
